{"thag6.14:0.1":"Theragatha 6.14 ","thag6.14:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thag6.14:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag6.14:0.4":"Sabbakamittheragatha ","thag6.14:1.1":"“Dvipadakoyam asuci, ","thag6.14:1.2":"duggandho parihirati; ","thag6.14:1.3":"Nanakunapaparipuro, ","thag6.14:1.4":"vissavanto tato tato. ","thag6.14:2.1":"Migam nilinam kutena, ","thag6.14:2.2":"baliseneva ambujam; ","thag6.14:2.3":"Vanaram viya lepena, ","thag6.14:2.4":"badhayanti puthujjanam. ","thag6.14:3.1":"Rupa sadda rasa gandha, ","thag6.14:3.2":"photthabba ca manorama; ","thag6.14:3.3":"Panca kamaguna ete, ","thag6.14:3.4":"itthirupasmi dissare. ","thag6.14:4.1":"Ye eta upasevanti, ","thag6.14:4.2":"rattacitta puthujjana; ","thag6.14:4.3":"Vaddhenti katasim ghoram, ","thag6.14:4.4":"acinanti punabbhavam. ","thag6.14:5.1":"Yo ceta parivajjeti, ","thag6.14:5.2":"sappasseva pada siro; ","thag6.14:5.3":"Somam visattikam loke, ","thag6.14:5.4":"sato samativattati. ","thag6.14:6.1":"Kamesvadinavam disva, ","thag6.14:6.2":"nekkhammam datthu khemato; ","thag6.14:6.3":"Nissato sabbakamehi, ","thag6.14:6.4":"patto me asavakkhayo”ti. ","thag6.14:6.5":"… Sabbakamitthero …. ","thag6.14:6.6":"Chakkanipato nitthito. ","thag6.14:7.0":"Tatruddanam ","thag6.14:7.1":"Uruvelakassapo ca, ","thag6.14:7.2":"thero tekicchakari ca; ","thag6.14:7.3":"Mahanago ca kullo ca, ","thag6.14:7.4":"malukyo sappadasako; ","thag6.14:7.5":"Katiyano migajalo, ","thag6.14:7.6":"jento sumanasavhayo; ","thag6.14:7.7":"Nhatamuni brahmadatto, ","thag6.14:7.8":"sirimando sabbakami ca; ","thag6.14:7.9":"Gathayo caturasiti, ","thag6.14:7.10":"thera cettha catuddasati. "}